  "bodyText": "You should complete the calculator in one go. At the moment, it is not possible to save your answers and come back to them later.\n\nThis tool only gives an **estimate** based on the Severance Payments Act (Cap. 355A). Your contract of employment may entitle you to more. It is not legal advice.\n\n## How long does it take?\n\nAbout 3 minutes.\n\n## What you will need\n\nHave these ready before you start:\n\n- why you were sent home (redundancy, disaster, lay-off or short time, or death of employer)\n- your start date and your last day at work\n- your usual gross pay (weekly or monthly) — include overtime or bonuses\n\n<a data-start-link href=\"/money-financial-support/calculate-severance-pay/form\">Start your estimate now</a>"
